process_txt: Activate Sakura-Tribe Elder by sacrificing it, searching your library for a basic Plains and put it onto the battlefield tapped.
The Plains enters the battlefield, triggering Emeria Shepherd, returning Sakura-Tribe Elder from your graveyard to the battlefield.
combo.require_txt:
Emeria Shepherd must be on the battlefield.
Sakura-Tribe Elder must be on the battlefield.
combo.results_txt: Put all basic Plains from your library onto the battlefield.

description:
Result: Put all basic Plains from your library onto the battlefield.

        Requires: Emeria Shepherd must be on the battlefield.
Sakura-Tribe Elder must be on the battlefield.


        Steps:
        Activate Sakura-Tribe Elder by sacrificing it, searching your library for a basic Plains and put it onto the battlefield tapped.
The Plains enters the battlefield, triggering Emeria Shepherd, returning Sakura-Tribe Elder from your graveyard to the battlefield.
Repeat.
